<h2 id="notes">Notes</h2>

<p>Gerald quotes:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Dictators are allergic to reform, and they are cunning survivors. They will do whatever it takes to preserve their power and wealth, no matter how much blood ends up on their hands. They are master deceivers and talented manipulators who cannot be trusted to change. <cite>George Ayittey</cite></p>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="credits">Credits</h2>

<h3 id="performed-by">Performed by</h3>

<dl>
  <dt>Gerald Duchene</dt>
  <dd>all instrumentation</dd>
  <dt>Dan Ecclestone</dt>
  <dd>vocals and melody</dd>
  <dt>Simone Silvestroni</dt>
  <dd>bass</dd>
</dl>

